Package: bushfireRisk
Type: Package
Title: Australian Bushfire Risk Analysis and Visualization
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sravan Kumar", "Kapu Bejjala", 
                  email = "sravan.kapu@example.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides tools and data for analyzing the attribution 
    of Australian bushfire risk to anthropogenic climate change. It includes 
    cleaned datasets, analysis functions, and an interactive Shiny application 
    for exploring bushfire risk patterns across Australian regions, particularly 
    focusing on the 2019-2020 Black Summer fires and the Forest Fire Danger Index (FFDI).
